  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Get ready for furious fighting action with ULTIMATE FIGHTER! The evil enemy made a raid on Rick's master's training school, took symbols and swords away, and left a letter of challenge behind. Rick, having vowed to be a true fighter, took up this challenge to win back the lost items.\n\nSharpen your fighting skills and prepare for devastating, bonecrushing battles. Rick's fate is in your hands. The challenge addressed to him is also made to you. The success of his quest depends on your courage, cunning, and flawless martial arts technique.",
